           We created a custom responsive webpage for a simpler user
            experience, while staying consistent with the brand
            vision. We've done a lot of research and made sure our website meets its main goal: educate, inform teenagers about HIV and AIDS. 
            The biggest challenge we had to face is how to clearly communicate important and serious information without overwhelming the potential user.
            We used calm pastel but yet bright colors, a lot of "real-people" imagery, and real-life interviewing to connect and start the conversation.
